{"tid":2094572,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"同大家分享下英國嘅地道俚語(slang)","createTime":"2020-07-04T17:50:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T04:18:16.000Z","uid":127898,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c26b853385d8ff07065b9cc53fc1600d60066717","tid":2094572,"uid":127898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T17:50:42.000Z","msg":"講翻少少背景先 我係英國South West 住左十年左右 🇬🇧<br />\n中學讀政府學校 大學同幾個local 一齊住 畢業後留左係到做嘢 住左咁耐學左唔少slang 想同大家分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講明先 以下係我自己平時會周不時用到嘅slang, 當然係英國亦會有唔同地區會有自已嘅regional slang (例如: Cockney rhyming slang) <br />\n<br />\n我以下所分享嘅slang 有啲係用左幾十年，甚至乎過百年,唔同年齡嘅英國人都會理解嗰個slang 點解<br />\n<br />\n而有啲slang 係近代嘅&rsquo;潮語&rsquo; , 所以係英國年紀比較大嘅人未必會用到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />某啲住係英國其他地方嘅巴絲打可能都未必用過/聽過<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>Aite/ What you sayin&rsquo; / Wag one</strong></span>  <br />\n<br />\n以上嘅phrase 都係同其他人打招呼用到，英國人好少會講&rsquo;Hello, how are you?&rsquo; (通常接電話先會講hello, 好似我地接電話講&rsquo;喂&rsquo;) <br />\n<br />\n最常用係&rsquo;alright?&rsquo;, 有時候會簡化到得 &lsquo;Aite?&rsquo;一個音<br />\n我見到同事通常會講&rsquo;You alright?/ alright mate?&rsquo; <br />\n回答可以講&rsquo;yeah, you?&rsquo; (即係我很好，你呢？) <br />\n<br />\n如果有人問你&rsquo;alright?&rsquo; 你亦都可以好簡單咁答翻&rsquo;alright?&rsquo;<br />\n<br />\n&lsquo;What you sayin&rsquo; 同 &lsquo;wag one&rsquo; 係我同其他同年紀嘅朋友常用嘅greetings, 直接譯過黎雖然唔make sense 但係其實意思同hello 一樣, 回答嘅方法可以好似alright咁repeat 返佢講what you sayin&rsquo;/ wag one<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>Innit</strong></span> <br />\n<br />\n&lsquo;Innit&rsquo; 係我自己成日用嘅slang , 意思即係&rsquo;isn&rsquo;t it?&rsquo; <br />\n<br />\n&lsquo;Innit&rsquo;係用嚟表示認同，類似係&lsquo;I agree&rsquo; 嘅意思<br />\n<br />\n例如當你個朋友話:<br />\n&lsquo;This club is dead as fuck&rsquo; <br />\n(哩個club 唔係好掂喎) <br />\n你就可以答<br />\n&lsquo;Innit&rsquo; <br />\n(咪係囉) <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>Peng</strong></span> <br />\n<br />\n&lsquo;Peng&rsquo; 係近年非常之popular ，意思係指&rsquo;beautiful&rsquo; <br />\n可以形容一個地方，食物或者形容一個人(通常係女性) <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>Butters/ Buzz</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n&lsquo;Butters&rsquo; 係 &lsquo;peng&rsquo; 嘅相反，好似&rsquo;ugly&rsquo; 咁解 , 後生嘅好中意用<br />\n(不過通常形容一個人)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>Ting</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n&lsquo;Ting&rsquo; 係&rsquo;thing&rsquo; 嘅簡稱<br />\n可以百搭任用，後生嘅亦都好中意用<br />\n<br />\nE.g.<br />\n&lsquo;Mate, can you gimme that ting on the table?&rsquo; <br />\n你可唔可比枱上面嗰舊嘢比我？<br />\n<br />\n&lsquo;She&rsquo;s a peng ting&rsquo; <br />\n(She is a beautiful girl)<br />\n<br />\n&lsquo;He looked butters last night&rsquo;<br />\n(He did not look attractive last night)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>Chav</strong></span><br />\n&lsquo;Chav&rsquo; 係形容一個&rsquo;死窮鬼&rsquo; , 通常係指一啲working class 嘅人，有貶意食份<br />\n<br />\n&lsquo;What&rsquo;s with these trainers? You look like a chav today&rsquo; <br />\n(你對鞋發生咩事？你今日着到好似死窮鬼咁) <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Mate/ Fella/ Fam / Bruv/ Mush/ G </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n以上所有字詞都係差唔多同一個meaning, 都可以loosely 解作&rsquo;朋友&rsquo; <br />\n<br />\nE.g.<br />\n&lsquo;Alrite mate&rsquo; <br />\n<br />\n&lsquo;What you sayin&rsquo; fam&rsquo;<br />\n<br />\n&lsquo;Wag one g&rsquo; <br />\n<br />\n&lsquo;See you later bruv&rsquo; <br />\n<br />\n&lsquo;Alright mush?&rsquo; <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>Skank</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n&lsquo;Skank&rsquo; 同&rsquo;slut&rsquo; 差唔多意思<br />\n<br />\n好似我地所講嘅&rsquo;公廁&rsquo; <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>Bird/ Lassie</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n&lsquo;Bird&rsquo; 同 &lsquo;lassie&rsquo; 都係指一位年輕女子<br />\n<br />\n&lsquo;Bird&rsquo; 有少少貶意成份<br />\n<br />\nE.g. <br />\n&lsquo;Mate!!!! That bird I was with last week was a proper skank! I just found out I got STD from her!&rsquo; <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>Feds</strong></span><br />\n<br />\nFeds= Police <br />\n<br />\nE.g.<br />\n&lsquo;The Feds were looking for you&rsquo; <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>Shag</strong></span><br />\n<br />\nShag = 扑野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nE.g.<br />\n&lsquo;I shagged that bird last night&rsquo; <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陣間唸到咩再同大家分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80159576db0f54e7d234f892ca531393974e2860","tid":2094572,"uid":58335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T17:52:14.000Z","msg":"多謝分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無意得罪<br />\n不過好似美國地道俚語過癮D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31803c600209777b5835b47c6d4ea6da9b9c75c0","tid":2094572,"uid":276609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T17:52:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d3ad4dea0ab44528677b7813e1a967ae61432cff","tid":2094572,"uid":229100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T17:53:12.000Z","msg":"Mother fucker最常用 <br />\n同開英國佬做野傾計 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f32af60cd712eb7d2987eeca0b826cbe9699da7b","tid":2094572,"uid":127898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T17:53:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>Dutch oven</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n直譯係&rsquo;荷蘭焗爐&rsquo; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而實際上係解當你同你條女訓教個陣你係張被放屁，之後夾硬塞佢個頭逼鳩佢閒你啲屁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>Grim/Minging</strong></span><br />\n<br />\nRank/ Grim/ Minging = horrible <br />\n<br />\nE.g.<br />\n&lsquo;Carrie slapped me hard after I gave her Dutch oven this morning. Judging from her face I could tell it was minging&rsquo; <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>Bare</strong></span><br />\n<br />\nBare= extremely, a lot of (好多) <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>Bread</strong></span><br />\n<br />\nBread = money <br />\n<br />\nE.g.<br />\n<br />\nHis family has bare bread.<br />\n(His family has a lot of money) <br />\n<br />\nI was bare tired after last night&rsquo;s shag.<br />\n(I was exhausted after sleeping with him / her last night) <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>野食篇</strong></span><br />\n<br />\nMaccies = 麥記<br />\n<br />\nChippy = 炸魚薯條鋪<br />\n<br />\nSpoons = Wetherspoons = 英國最大型嘅連鎖酒吧，好似香港嘅大快活咁<br />\n<br />\nCuppa = cup of <br />\n大部分英國人一日飲奶茶飲到黑，平時返工或者去人地屋企好多時都會比人offer 問想唔想飲杯tea, 你亦可以offer 人地 &lsquo;cuppa tea&rsquo; <br />\n<br />\nE.g.<br />\n&lsquo;Do you fancy a cuppa tea?&rsquo; <br />\n&lsquo;Do you wanna come in for a cuppa?&rsquo; <br />\n<br />\nFag = cigarettes 🚬 <br />\n<br />\nE.g. <br />\n&lsquo;Can I borrow a fag?&rsquo;"},{"pid":"0c673d9002f4d5b3eace05857643b1ef1379951e","tid":2094572,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T17:54:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a56b7dd3b9088184b8ee997ce868859f166c1c3","tid":2094572,"uid":24981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c673d9002f4d5b3eace05857643b1ef1379951e","tid":2094572,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T17:54:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T17:55:38.000Z","msg":"Bob"},{"pid":"11c2116282ae45443c189854e96aa17485397d5c","tid":2094572,"uid":127898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80159576db0f54e7d234f892ca531393974e2860","tid":2094572,"uid":58335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T17:52:14.000Z","msg":"多謝分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無意得罪<br />\n不過好似美國地道俚語過癮D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T17:56:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n美國嗰啲我唔識<br />\n<br />\n你可以考慮開post 教下大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00f51df3783e3ca5054789611ac21ab83f76e94f","tid":2094572,"uid":127898,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0c673d9002f4d5b3eace05857643b1ef1379951e","tid":2094572,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T17:54:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T18:00:02.000Z","msg":"相比之下 <br />\n<br />\n&lsquo;Bob&rsquo;s your uncle&rsquo; 係一啲catch phrase , 已經有好耐歷史<br />\n<br />\n其實仲有下一句<br />\n<br />\n&lsquo;Bob&rsquo;s your uncle, Fanny&rsquo;s your aunt&rsquo;"},{"pid":"b03f305229b99c4a409404f49166b84dda70514c","tid":2094572,"uid":326758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T18:11:20.000Z","msg":"聽過you alright讀到似yoi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />load咗陣講乜"},{"pid":"f4aa54453b142fcba403099869f9af490d41767e","tid":2094572,"uid":336872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T18:36:03.000Z","msg":"留名學野～"},{"pid":"30fc05ffaeda44079d4bace27da99cdf2403bca7","tid":2094572,"uid":56541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T18:36:40.000Z","msg":"推，仲有冇咩生活小細節呀，當地人先會明嘅inside joke呀嗰啲"},{"pid":"245dae1933420556021d28830f827442205d581c","tid":2094572,"uid":56541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30fc05ffaeda44079d4bace27da99cdf2403bca7","tid":2094572,"uid":56541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T18:36:40.000Z","msg":"推，仲有冇咩生活小細節呀，當地人先會明嘅inside joke呀嗰啲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T18:36:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8b8d397f8dd110bec1b2dea34fc444e9c1980df7","tid":2094572,"uid":183460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T18:45:08.000Z","msg":"呢d 好岩洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6227d0f4199bcb8ecb7b552b4f22e1ffe5c3c2c2","tid":2094572,"uid":39268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T18:58:43.000Z","msg":"幾有趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33b8d50b5b5e3a9f70c88947d3604e40471632cc","tid":2094572,"uid":130228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T04:18:16.000Z","msg":"有用post"}]}